name: Hati and Skoll
description:
According to the prophecy of the Völvas, on the day of Ragnarok they will catch up and absorb both Salt and Mani. In the meantime, they serve as motivation for the luminaries to quickly and accurately follow their orbits.

Minted 12/9/21 for #OBJKT4OBJKT and also 1k followers on my twitter.
